data.description: Stately home overlooking  cul-de-sac * Beautiful front patio * Spacious home with upgrades throughout* TWO additions: Game room off of the lower level & Work room/shed off back of the garage * Primary bedroom has newer barn doors leading into the walk in closet and primary bathroom * Both bathrooms and the half bathroom have been remodeled * Enjoy cozy winter nights by the gas fireplace (firebox & new remote replaced 2 years ago) * Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite counters and backsplash * Barn doors lead into private bar area in lower level---great for entertaining or an easy conversion to great home office or bedroom * Wall mounted televisions will stay with the house* Clothes Washer and Dryer replaced in 2022* Garage doors replaced 2019 * A/C replaced in 2018 * HWH 2018 * Gutters replaced 2018*
